This Automation suite uses below tools and libraries

1, Rest Assured
2, Maven
3, Java


To Use the Framework, Follow below mentioned steps

1, Open/Import the suite in Eclipse
2, Right Click on below mentioned xml files from the project and click on Run As -> TestNG Suite
	-AllTests.xml
	-Products.xml
	-Categories.xml
	-Service.xml
	-Stores.xml
	
To View Test Report
	
1, Go to project folder in your drive.
2, Open Test-Output Folder
3, Click on Index.html it will open report in browser.



